<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link href="css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <script src="js/jquery-3.3.1.js"></script>
    <script src="js/scripts.js"></script>
    <title>Where Should I Go?</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Where should you spend your next vacation?</h1>
    <p>Do you, like many, have trouble making decisions?  Then let a fake internet eight ball make major life decisions for you!</p>
    <p>Introducing the Magiceightcation!  In 5 simple questions, it will decide where you fly!</p>
    <p>Just answer a few simple questions, hit the MAGICEIGHTCATION button, and away you go!</p>
    <div class="container">
      <form>
        <h2>What Do You Want to See?</h2>
        <select class="form-control" id="location">
          <option>Mountains</option>
          <option>City</option>
          <option>Ocean</option>
          <option>Desert</option>
        </select>
        <div class="radio">
          <label>
            <input type="radio" name="temperature" value="hot as the sun" checked>
            Hot as the Sun
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="radio">
          <label>
          <input type="radio" name="flavor" value="antarctic">
          Antarctic
        </label>
        </div>
        <div class="radio">
          <label>
          <input type="radio" name="flavor" value="average">
          Average
          </label>
        </div>
        <p>Do you like to be far from home?</p>
        <select id="distance">
          <option value="yes">Yes</option>
          <option value="no">No</option>
        </select>
        <p>Do you like to be far from home?</p>
        <select id="swim">
          <option value="yes">Yes</option>
          <option value="no">No</option>
          </select>
        <p>Which shoes do you want to wear?  Heels, snowboots, or flip flops?</p>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="shoes">Shoes?</label>
            <input id="shoes" class="form-control" type="text">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn">Magiceightcation Me!</button>
      </form>


      <div id="under-21">
        <h1>Sorry, we can't serve you.</h1>

        <p>It's illegal in the US. Try Mexico or Europe.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
